your blood is flowing faster you realize ♪

00:06:49.949 --> 00:06:57.999 line:1
♪ That when you come together you 
will open like a blossom to a butterfly. ♪

00:06:59.373 --> 00:07:00.793 line:1
[guitar strumming]

00:07:03.008 --> 00:07:07.518 line:1
♪ Rochester your horses 
know the secrets of the grasses. ♪

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:12.699 line:1
♪ They learn about forever with 
each tender shoot that passes. ♪

00:07:13.276 --> 00:07:17.606 line:1
♪ The heat beneath their 
rippling skin is rising in the twilight. ♪

00:07:18.534 --> 00:07:23.084 line:1
♪ And when you come together you 
